{"tid":2043082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【向盟友學習】港式鬥黃vs西式鬥黃","createTime":"2020-05-30T07:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T00:35:17.000Z","uid":131691,"like":248,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff0bd25d71937017245a33828a1316d12e59a45","tid":2043082,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"TL;DR:<br />\n港式鬥黃=你唔夠我黃，所以你要死<br />\n西式鬥黃=你覺得你好黃咩？我一於黃過你俾你睇！<br />\n<br />\n「鬥黃」呢樣嘢基本上由「黃色經濟圈出現後」已經變成某部分香港人嘅陋習，其實內裡核心同早前「捉鬼」一樣：凡事做判官，覺得人哋唔夠自己把尺，就開大火候攻擊，目的係鞏固自己現有地位。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如是者，人哋死咗，自己冇變，個Overton Window冇推進到，甚至倒退。</strong><br />\n<br />\n相反，西方近日嘅「鬥黃」個核心完全唔同：凡事都係做判官，但係當覺得人哋唔夠黃嘅時候，自己會踏出再多一步，用表態、言論、甚至行為示範俾「唔夠黃」嘅人睇：嗱，咁先夠黃㗎嘛！你好追上嚟啦，如果唔係會做被時代拋棄嘅垃圾㗎啦！<br />\n<br />\nTrump vs Biden又係咁，英國美國兩大黨互相鬥又係咁，各報社又係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如是者，人哋有咗動力去追上自己原有位置，自己又再進化，成個Overton Window向更加黃進發。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋香港人一齊向各地嘅盟友學習下啦，好嘛？</span>"},{"pid":"764e36d63f093f0356aa1c88a36020dfebbdb068","tid":2043082,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c8895864a0d6a47430588d676dfe496141671f","tid":2043082,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb0ea97b236aa509099a62738e9676bd5fc6efc","tid":2043082,"uid":95138,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"港式不鬥黃、不分化：<br />\n食藍店 = 展現民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QnUDcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail